an]]<ref>{{cite news|last1=L\u00f3pez Rejas|first1=Javier|title=Knut Urban: \"Los \u00e1tomos han dejado de ser un campo ex\u00f3tico\"|url=http://www.elcultural.es/revista/ciencia/Knut-Urban-Los-atomos-han-dejado-de-ser-un-campo-exotico/34564|accessdate=5 February 2015|publisher=[[El Cultural]]|date=May 2, 2014}}</ref>\n| {{Flagu|Germany}}\n| Basic Sciences\n|\n|-\n| 2013\n| [[Adrian Bird]]<ref>{{cite news|last1=S\u00e1nchez-Monge|first1=Mar\u00eda|title=Adrian Bird: \"Soy como un hereje de la epigen\u00e9tica\"|url=http://www.diariomedico.com/2014/06/23/area-cientifica/especialidades/genetica/soy-como-hereje-epigenetica|accessdate=5 February 2015|publisher=Diario M\u00e9dico|date=June 23, 2014}}</ref>\n| {{Flagu|United Kingdom}}\n| Biomedicine\n|\n|-\n| 2013\n| [[Paul R. Ehrlich]]<ref>{{cite news|title=Fundaci\u00f3n BBVA premia a Paul Ehrlich por sus estudios sobre biodiversidad|url=http://www.lavanguardia.com/vida/20140204/54399892220/fundacion-bbva-premia-a-ehrlich-por-sus-investigaciones-sobre-biodiversidad.html|accessdate=5 February 2015|publisher=La vanguardia|date=February 4, 2014}}</ref>\n| {{Flagu|United States}}\n| Ecology and Conservation Biology\n|\n|-\n| 2013\n| [[Marvin Minsky]]<ref>{{cite news|last1=Elola|first1=Joseba|title=Nadie est\u00e1 al frente del planeta|url=http://cultura.elpais.com/cultura/2014/08/29/actualidad/1409308709_665686.html|accessdate=5 February 2015|publisher=El Pa\u00eds (Grupo PRISA)|date=August 31, 2014}}</ref>\n| {{Flagu|United States}}\n| Information and Communication Technologies\n|\n|-\n| 2013\n| [[Elhanan Helpman]]<ref>{{cite news|last1=Cymerman|first1=Henrique|title=Es probable que veamos m\u00e1s protestas y m\u00e1s presi\u00f3n para que se hagan cambios|url=http://www.lavanguardia.com/magazine/20140613/54409763142/entrevista-elhanan-helpman-israel-europa-economia-magazine.html|accessdate=5 February 2015|publisher=Magazine La Vanguardia|date=June 13, 2014}}</ref>\n| {{Flagu|Israel}}\n| Economics, Finance and Managemen