es Sawyers]]<ref>{{cite news|title=Los pioneros del tratamiento personalizado del c\u00e1ncer, premio Fundaci\u00f3n BBVA|url=http://www.lavanguardia.com/vida/20150127/54424016736/los-pioneros-del-tratamiento-personalizado-del-cancer-premio-fundacion-bbva.html|accessdate=5 February 2015|publisher=La Vanguardia|date=January 27, 2014}}</ref>\n| {{Flagu|United States}}\n| Biomedicine\n|\n|-\n| 2014\n| [[Anthony R. Hunter|Tony Hunter]]<ref>{{cite news|title=Medicina personalizada contra el c\u00e1ncer|url=http://elpais.com/elpais/2015/02/04/buenavida/1423064348_568607.html|accessdate=5 February 2015|publisher=El Pa\u00eds (Grupo PRISA9|date=February 4, 2015}}</ref>\n| {{Flagu|United Kingdom}}\n| Biomedicine\n|\n|-\n| 2014\n| [[David Tilman]]<ref>{{cite news|last1=Mosquera|first1=Eva|title=Premio al pionero que demostr\u00f3 el valor de la biodiversidad|url=http://www.elmundo.es/ciencia/2015/02/03/54d0c962268e3e301e8b458e.html|accessdate=5 February 2015|publisher=El Mundo|date=February 3, 2015}}</ref>\n| {{Flagu|United States}}\n| Ecology and Conservation Biology\n|\n|-\n| 2014\n| [[Leonard Kleinrock]]<ref>{{cite news|title=El art\u00edfice de la primera conexi\u00f3n de datos en internet,Premio Fundaci\u00f3n BBVA|url=http://www.lavanguardia.com/tecnologia/20150113/54423316976/el-artifice-de-la-primera-conexion-de-datos-en-internet-premio-fundacion-bbva.html|accessdate=5 February 2015|publisher=La Vanguardia|date=January 13, 2015}}</ref>\n| {{Flagu|United States}}\n| Information and Communication Technologies\n|\n|-\n| 2014\n| [[Richard Blundell]]\n| {{Flagu|United Kingdom}}\n| Economics, Finance and Management\n|\n|-\n| 2014\n| [[David Card]]\n| {{Flagu|Canada}}\n| Economics, Finance and Management\n|\n|-\n| 2014\n| [[Gy\u00f6rgy Kurt\u00e1g]]<ref>{{cite news|last1=Leticia|first1=Yustos|title=Gy\u00f6rgy Kurt\u00e1g premio Fundaci\u00f3n BBVA Fronteras del Conocimiento en la especialidad de m\u00fasica contempor\u00e1nea|url=http://www.docenotas.com/121656/gyorgy-kurtag-premio-fundacion-bbva-fronteras-del-conocimiento-en-la-especialidad-de-musica-contemporanea/|accessdate=11 February 2015|publisher=Doce Notas|date=February 10, 2015}}</ref>\n| {{Flagu|Hungary}}\n| Contemporary Music\n|\n|-\n| 2014\n| [[Richard Alley]]<ref>{{cite news|last1=Acosta|first1=A.|title=El glaci\u00f3logo Richard Alley, premio Fronteras del Conocimiento de Cambio Clim\u00e1tico|url=http://www.abc.es/sociedad/20150109/abci-richard-alley-premio-bbva-201501091333.html|accessdate=5 February 2015|publisher=ABC|date=January 9, 2015}}</ref>\n| {{Flagu|United States}}\n| Climate Change\n|\n|-\n| 2014\n| [[Helen Keller International]]\n| {{Flagu|United States}}\n| Development Cooperation\n|\n|-\n| 2015\n| [[Stephen Hawking]]\n| {{Flagu|United Kingdom}}\n| Basic Sciences\n|-\n| 2015\n| [[Viatcheslav Mukhanov]]\n| {{Flagu|Germany}}\n| Basic Sciences\n|-\n| 2015\n| [[Edward Boyden]]\n| {{Flagu|United States}}\n| Biomedicine\n|-\n| 2015\n| [[Karl Deisseroth]]\n| {{Flagu|United States}}\n| Biomedicine\n|-\n| 2015\n| [[Gero Miesenb\u00f6ck]]\n| {{Flagu|Austria}}\n| Biomedicine\n|-\n| 2015\n| [[Ilkka Hanski]]\n| {{Flagu|Finland}}\n| Ecology and Conservation Biology\n|-\n| 2015\n| [[Stephen Cook]]\n| {{Flagu|Canada}}\n| Information and Communication Technologies\n|-\n| 2015\n| [[Robert B. Wilson|Robert Wilson]]\n| {{Flagu|United States}}\n| Economics, Finance and Management\n|-\n| 2015\n| [[Georges Aperghis]]\n| {{Flagu|Greece}}\n| Contemporary Music\n|-\n| 2015\n| [[Veerabhadran Ramanathan]]\n| {{Flagu|India}}\n| Climate Change\n|-\n| 2015\n| [[Martin Ravallion]]\n| {{Flagu|Australia}}\n| Development Cooperation\n|-\n| 2016\n| [[David Cox (statistician)|David Cox]]\n| {{Flagu|United Kingdom}}\n| Basic Sciences\n|-\n| 2016\n| [[Bradley Efron]]\n| {{Flagu|United States}}\n| Basic Sciences\n|-\n| 2016\n| [[Emmanuelle Charpentier]]\n| {{Flagu|France}}\n| Biomedicine\n|-\n| 2016\n| [[Jennifer Doudna]]\n| {{Flagu|United States}}\n| Biomedicine\n|-\n| 2016\n| [[Francisco Mojica]]\n| {{Flagu|Spain}}\n| Biomedicine\n|-\n| 2016\n| [[Gene E. Likens]]\n| {{Flagu|United States}}\n| Ecology and Conservation Biology\n|-\n| 2016\n| [[Marten Scheffer]]\n| {{Flagu|Netherlands}}\n| Ecology and Conservation Biology\n|-\n| 2016\n| [[Geoffrey Hinton]]\n| {{Flagu|United Kingdom}}\n| Information and Communication Technologies\n|-\n| 2016\n| [[Daron Acemoglu]]\n| {{Flagu|Turkey}} / {{Flagu|United States}}\n| Economics, Finance and Management\n|-\n| 2016\n| [[Sofia Gubaidulina]]\n| {{Flagu|Russia}}\n| Contemporary Music\n|-\n| 2016\n| [[James Hansen]]\n| {{Flagu|United States}}\n| Climate Change\n| Economic Sciences 2013\n|-\n| 2016\n| [[Syukuro Manabe]]\n| {{Flagu|Japan}} / {{Flagu|United States}}\n| Climate Change\n|-\n| 2017\n| [[Omar M. Yaghi]]\n| {{Flagu|Jordan}} / {{Flagu|United States}}\n| Basic Sciences\n|-\n| 2017\n| [[James P. Allison]]\n| {{Flagu|United States}}\n| Biomedicine\n| Medicine 2018\n|-\n| 2017\n| [[Rosemary Grant]]\n| {{Flagu|United Kingdom}}\n| Ecology and Conservation Biology\n|-\n| 2017\n| [[Peter and Rosemary Grant|Peter Grant]]\n| {{Flagu|United Kingdom}}\n| Ecology and Conservation Biology\n|-\n| 2017\n| [[Shafi Goldwasser]]\n| {{Flagu|United States}}\n| Information and Communication Technologies\n|-\n| 2017\n| [[Silvio Micali]]\n| {{Flagu|Italy}}\n| Information and Communication Technologies\n|-\n| 2017\n| [[Ronald Rivest]]\n| {{Flagu|United States}}\n| Information and Communication Technologies\n|-\n| 2017\n| [[Adi Shamir]]\n| {{Flagu|Israel}}\n| Information and Communication Technologies\n|-\n|2017\n|{{Interlanguage link|Robert Porter (economist)|lt=Robert Porter|ru|\u041f\u043e\u0440\u0442\u0435\u0440, \u0420\u043e\u0431\u0435\u0440\u0442}}\n|{{Flagu|Canada}}\n|Economics Finance and Management\n|-\n|2017\n|[[Ari\u00e9l Pakes|Ariel Pakes]]\n|{{Flagu|Canada}} / {{Flagu|United States}}\n|Economics Finance and Management\n|-\n|2017\n|{{Interlanguage link|Timothy Bresnahan|d|Q41799775}}\n|{{Flagu|United States}}\n|Economics Finan